  <original-body>Although AR::Relation provides `to_json`, it still can't be encoded with `ActiveSupport::JSON.encode` because the latter detects a circular reference and errors out. So, this is not possible:

    # controller action
    render :json =&gt; relation

[I fixed it](http://github.com/mislav/rails/commit/59a4fe0a098b388f70255bc6140a60ab9ceea9b3) by providing `as_json` method in AR::Relation.</original-body>
